 toldBBCSport: 'No and I have to say that it's a little bit unfair to the athletes themselves.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the delay\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You get yourself to that arousal point where you are in the zone, you are absolutely wanting to give everything and then that is just waining slightly, the longer you are left out there.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that arousal point\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"the zone\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is the finite margins we are talking about and that for me was just way too long.'\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finite margins\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill, meanwhile, argued that the delay may actually have made for a more exciting race.\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2519, \"end\": 2537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the delay\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"a more exciting race\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But then I suppose just look at the times,' the London 2012 hero said in response to Lewis' comments.\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.99999999993